            "description": "Register a donor to a campaign. If donor doesn't exist, creates them. Uses smart registration logic with transaction support.\n\n**Smart Registration Logic:**\n- If nationalId found: links existing donor\n- If not found + full details (name, phone) provided: creates new donor\n- If not found + missing details: throws error\n- If found + new details provided: updates donor info\n- offlineSyncId: auto-generated if not provided"
